### =========================================
### 1️⃣ Create User
### =========================================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ashish",
  "email": "ashish@test.com"
}

###

### =========================================
### 2️⃣ Get All Users
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/all

###

### =========================================
### 3️⃣ Seed Test Conversations
### Replace USER_ID with real ID from step 1
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/seed?userId=69982b3d9a01970f37c4cd7f

###

### =========================================
### 4️⃣ Test RAG Directly (Vector Search Only)
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/rag-test?message=Should%20I%20give%20discount?

###

### =========================================
### 5️⃣ Full Chat Flow (RAG + LLM)
### Replace USER_ID with real ID
### =========================================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID",
  "message": "Client asking for discount. What should I do?"
}

###

### =========================================
### 6️⃣ RAG Test - Vector Search Results
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/rag-test?userId=69982b3d9a01970f37c4cd7f&message=discount

### =========================================
### 7️⃣ RAG Context - Formatted for LLM
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/rag-context?userId=69982b3d9a01970f37c4cd7f&message=How%20to%20handle%20refunds?

###


POST http://localhost:5000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "69982b3d9a01970f37c4cd7f",
  "message": "Should I give discount?",
  "category": "pricing"
}



### Create User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

###

### Seed conversations (replace USER_ID with the ID from above)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/seed?userId=69983e7eb7dbf5a7aec16edf

###

### Chat endpoint (replace USER_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "69983e7eb7dbf5a7aec16edf",
  "message": "Should I give discount?",
  "category": "pricing"
}

###

### Test with more specific message
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "69983e7eb7dbf5a7aec16edf",
  "message": "Should I give discount to loyal customers?",
  "category": "pricing"
}